      "_type": "text",
      "contents": "\n\n(** ** Continuity *)\n\n(** Definition of a continuous function depending on two uniform structures. *)\n"
    },
    {
      "_type": "sentence",
      "contents": "Definition IsContinuous\n  {X Y : Type} {usX : UStructure X} {usY : UStructure Y} (p : X -> Y)\n  := forall (u : X) (m : nat),\n      {n : nat & forall v : X, u =[n] v -> p u =[m] p v}.",
